<p style="margin: 0px;">Bank&nbsp;of&nbsp;America is committed to offering work place options that enhances associate satisfaction, the ability to competitively attract and retain associates and meet our business needs. We are also committed to environmental leadership in our communities. By reducing associate commutes and developing satellite buildings that are environmentally friendly, we are able to reduce fuel consumption and greenhouse gas emissions across the country.
<br><br>
Through our commitment to provide associates and their managers more flexibility in when and where to do business, My Work:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>allows associates to work where they can be most efficient and productive</li>
	<li>reinforces a performance-based culture where the "how and what" are primary success measures</li>
	<li>supports connectivity to customers, partners and teammates through innovative communication and collaboration tools</li>
</ul>
<H2 class="p" style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; padding: 0px;"><span class="bd">How is My Work different from Telecommuting?</span></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">With My Work, associates are provided the opportunity to work from a variety of locations, including a primary site, other bank locations or from home instead of the traditional, dedicated cube or office. They are able to take advantage of a comprehensive provisioning policy that provides the tools and support necessary to work remotely and they also can be reimbursed for office expenses incurred as a flexible worker.
<br><br>
Note:  Not all positions are eligible for My Work. If you are interested in finding out more, please discuss the opportunity with your recruiter or hiring manager. Considerations include corporate information security and job requirements. 
</p>

